Jenna von Oÿ https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jenna_von_O%C3%BF 0 Jennifer Jean von Oÿ (born May 2, 1977) is an American actress and country music singer. She is best known for her role as Six LeMeure on the NBC sitcom Blossom and her role as Stevie Van Lowe on the UPN sitcom The Parkers.
